high_descs: Turn around and veer left to the kitchen table.
Pick up the head of lettuce on the table.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Place the lettuce in the fridge on the shelf above the bowl. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Place the lettuce in the right basin of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled head of lettuce in a sink.

high_descs: Go right and then right again to face the white table with the coffee maker on it.
Pick the lettuce up from the table.
Turn around and go left to face the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge and shut the door and then open it and pick the lettuce up and shut the door.
Go to the right and stand in front of the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce in a sink.

high_descs: Turn right and when you get to the end of the counter on your left, turn right again until you're in front of the square white table.
Pick up the head of lettuce from the table.
Carry the lettuce to the fridge, which is to your right.
Place the lettuce in the fridge on the top shelf on the right, close the door, and then remove the lettuce after a few seconds.
Turn right and carry the lettuce to the sink.
Place the lettuce in the right sink.
anns.task_desc: Place cold lettuce in the sink.
